50|$|The <b>quarter</b> <b>days</b> {{have been}} {{observed}} {{at least since the}} Middle Ages, and they ensured that debts and unresolved lawsuits were not allowed to linger on. Accounts had to be settled, a reckoning had to be made and publicly recorded on the <b>quarter</b> <b>days.</b>|$|R
